      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning buyer. Demonstrating exceptional mechanical integrity and a refined aesthetic, it has been serviced to rigorous standards to ensure continued performance and reliability. A superlative choice for those seeking the perfect balance of prestige and proven value.",
      "price": 34900.0,
