    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned VANOS variable valve timing system. This example remains mechanically sound with a reinforced rear subframe and a crisp-shifting 6-speed manual transmission feeding a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry utilizes aluminum control arms and a sophisticated multi-link rear setup for exceptional lateral grip. While the chassis shows minor signs of road use, the powertrain exhibits excellent compression and cooling efficiency. Recent service includes valve clearance adjustment and fluid analysis, ensuring this high-revving masterpiece is track-ready or canyon-capable.",
